sentence: how many buttercup kitchen are there in san francisco ?
sentence-with-vars: how many VARrest are there in VARcity ?
sql: select count(*) from LOCATION,RESTAURANT where LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID and LOCATION.CITY_NAME='san francisco' and RESTAURANT.NAME='buttercup kitchen'
sql-with-vars: select count(*) from LOCATION,RESTAURANT where LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID and LOCATION.CITY_NAME='VARcity' and RESTAURANT.NAME='VARrest'
